title: E126 LOGAN PAUL PROVES HE’S NOT A SOCIOPATH - IMPAULSIVE EP. 126
itunes:title: LOGAN PAUL PROVES HE’S NOT A SOCIOPATH - IMPAULSIVE EP. 126
description:
Logan reveals what was going through his mind when his lips were inches away from KSI at the press conference, and why John Cena made him cry. Also, the boys speak out on Six Nine’s snitching, Justin Trudeau’s leaked “brown face” picture, and the controversial and viral anti-school shooting PSA made by Sandy Hook Promise.
